paraphrases: Among the courses 482 and 485 , which 1 is more difficult ?
Between 482 and 485 , which course is harder ?
Between 482 and 485 , which course is more difficult ?
Given 482 and 485 , which course is harder ?
Which class is tougher among 482 and 485 ?
Which course among 482 and 485 is harder ?

sentence: Which course is harder between 482 and 485 ?
sentence-with-vars: Which course is harder between number0 and number1 ?
sql: SELECT COURSEalias0.NUMBER , PROGRAM_COURSEalias0.WORKLOAD FROM COURSE AS COURSEalias0 , PROGRAM_COURSE AS PROGRAM_COURSEalias0 WHERE ( COURSEalias0.NUMBER = 482 OR COURSEalias0.NUMBER = 485 ) AND COURSEalias0.DEPARTMENT = "eecs" AND PROGRAM_COURSEalias0.COURSE_ID = COURSEalias0.COURSE_ID ORDER BY PROGRAM_COURSEalias0.WORKLOAD DESC LIMIT 1 ;
sql-with-vars: SELECT COURSEalias0.NUMBER , PROGRAM_COURSEalias0.WORKLOAD FROM COURSE AS COURSEalias0 , PROGRAM_COURSE AS PROGRAM_COURSEalias0 WHERE ( COURSEalias0.NUMBER = number0 OR COURSEalias0.NUMBER = number1 ) AND COURSEalias0.DEPARTMENT = "department0" AND PROGRAM_COURSEalias0.COURSE_ID = COURSEalias0.COURSE_ID ORDER BY PROGRAM_COURSEalias0.WORKLOAD DESC LIMIT 1 ;
